      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an exceptional specimen of automotive excellence, this vehicle remains in pristine, showroom condition. Meticulously preserved and maintained to the most exacting standards, it offers an uncompromising experience for the discerning driver. Every surface and mechanical component reflects a level of care that is rarely encountered in the secondary market. This is an investment-grade acquisition for those who demand nothing less than absolute perfection.",
