    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly collector-grade vehicle that defies its age. This car has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled environment, and its condition reflects a 'no-expense-spared' ownership philosophy. The exterior paint retains its deep, factory luster with zero swirl marks, rock chips, or door dings; it has recently been treated with a multi-stage paint correction and a premium ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains in a time-capsule state. The premium leather seats show no bolster wear or creasing, the carpets are pristine, and it still carries that subtle factory-fresh scent. Every electronic component, from the infotainment system to the smallest ambient light, functions exactly as it did the day it left the showroom. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach. It comes with a thick binder of documented service history, proving oil changes every 3,000 miles and preventative maintenance performed well ahead of schedule. The engine bay is clean enough to eat off of, and the undercarriage is free of any corrosion or leaks. This sale includes all original keys, the window sticker, and a custom-fitted car cover. I welcome any third-party pre-purchase inspection to verify the exceptional state of this vehicle.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 21
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are pleased to present an automotive specimen of extraordinary caliber. This vehicle remains in impeccable showroom condition, characterized by a flawless exterior finish and an interior that retains its original factory integrity. Meticulously maintained and subjected to an exhaustive technical evaluation, this unit represents the pinnacle of its class. For the discerning enthusiast seeking a vehicle that transcends the typical pre-owned experience, this investment-grade offering delivers unrivaled aesthetics and mechanical precision. We invite you to inspect this benchmark of automotive excellence.",
      "price": 44500.0,
